doctype html
html(lang='en-GB')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    // The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags
    meta(name='keywords', content='bible todo list, King James holy bible, words of Jesus, commandments of Jesus, bible index, bible to do items')
    meta(name='description', content="An index of blog articles published on this website.")
    title Blog Index
    // Bootstrap
    link(href='../css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='../css/common_page.css', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='../css/blog_page.css', rel='stylesheet')
  body
    mixin BLOG_DATE(day,month,year)
      .text-right
        span.blog-day
          | &nbsp;#{day}&nbsp;
        span.blog-month
          | &nbsp;#{month}&nbsp;
        span.blog-year
          | &nbsp;#{year}&nbsp;
    include ../includes/root_page_menu.pug
    include ../includes/resource_page_header.pug
    main
      //
        Main content
        ==================================================
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-8
            h1 Blog Index
            hr.featurette-divider

            p
              | Through this blog I hope to give you a flavour of my Christian lifestyle.
              | I hope that you will find it informative and helpful as I share my journey
              | and pray that it will be a blessing to you.

            p.text-right
              b Tim Simpson
              br 
              span.badge.hashtag #ChristianDogWalker

            h2 2021

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2021/18-always-good-news.html", title="Always Good News") Always Good News
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Tired of hearing or reading bad news? Read the news that's always good news: The gospel of
                  | Jesus Christ!
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("14","APR","2021")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2021/17-learning-to-walk.html", title="Learning To Walk") Learning To Walk
              .panel-body
                div
                  | The Christian journey starts with being born again. We are then to learn to
                  | "walk in the Spirit" and be "Spirit led", just like Jesus.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("17","FEB","2021")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2021/16-listen-with-your-eyes.html", title="Listen With Your Eyes") Listen With Your Eyes
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Jesus only did what He saw the Father do.
                  | We need to listen to God with our eyes so that we can see what He wants to tell us.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("23","JAN","2021")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2021/15-my-first-vision.html", title="My First Vision") My First Vision
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Throughout the bible God speaks to people through visions and dreams.
                  | Find out what happened when I had my first vision.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("11","JAN","2021")

            h2 2020

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/14-the-greatest-gift.html", title="The Greatest Gift") The Greatest Gift
              .panel-body
                div
                  | How silently, how silently, the wondrous gift is given.
                  | So God imparts to human hearts the blessings of His heaven.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("31","DEC","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/13-jesus-at-the-centre.html", title="Jesus At the Centre") Jesus At the Centre
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Why we choose to put Jesus at the centre of everything we do, both as individuals
                  | and as a church.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("23","NOV","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/12-life-group-challenge.html", title="Life Group Challenge") Life Group Challenge
              .panel-body
                div
                  | God wants each of us to grow spiritually and reach spiritual maturity so here's the challenge we set out
                  | at our recent life group meeting.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("08","OCT","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/11-the-sun-shall-be-turned-into-darkness.html", title="The Sun Shall Be Turned Into Darkness") The Sun Shall Be Turned Into Darkness
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Bible prophecy is being fulfilled before our eyes in this generation
                  | as fires burn out of control around the globe!
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("14","SEP","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/10-the-love-of-god.html", title="The Love Of God") The Love Of God
              .panel-body
                div
                  | There is nothing like the love of God. Nothing compares to it.
                  | Oh, that the world would see and taste that the Lord is good.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("25","AUG","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/09-the-heavens-declare-him.html", title="The Heavens Declare Him") The Heavens Declare Him
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Attending the Astronomical Society at Hull University as a child got me hooked on staring at the night sky.
                  | As a Christian, I often find myself looking up to heaven, even during the day, knowing that one day I'll be there.
                  | Here's what I saw recently.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("16","AUG","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/08-grounded.html", title="Grounded") Grounded
              .panel-body
                div
                  | "Losing the plot" is not an option in life. We have to remain "grounded", whatever situation we find ourselves in. But how do you do that?
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("09","AUG","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/07-he-is-faithful.html", title="He Is Faithful") He Is Faithful
              .panel-body
                div
                  | How events unfolded one weekend back in July 2017 left
                  | me convinced that there are no coincidences in life, nothing that happens by chance, and that no matter what
                  | circumstances we find ourselves in, God is with us and remains faithful.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("23","JUL","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/06-under-attack.html", title="Under Attack") Under Attack
              .panel-body
                div
                  | It is not a matter of if an attack will come but rather when they will come.
                  | Attacks can come in many forms and rarely unfold as a single event. Often multiple things happen in
                  | rapid succession as the enemy seeks to overwhelm and undermine the faith of believers.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("17","JUL","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/05-promises-of-protection.html", title="Promises of Protection") Promises Of Protection
              .panel-body
                div
                  | During this uncertain time of the Corona virus, we have rested more than ever on God's promises of protection
                  | as described in the bible, in particular by Psalm 91. Why not make these promises yours too?
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("11","JUL","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/04-spiritual-warfare.html", title="Spiritual Warfare") Spiritual Warfare
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Many of the spiritual battles and attacks that spill over into the earthly realm often have an "earthly"
                  | explanation instead of being recognised as the work or influence of the evil one.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("04","JUL","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/03-all-change.html", title="All Change!") All Change!
              .panel-body
                div
                  | The onset of the COVID-19 Corona Virus as a world-wide pandemic has had a massive impact
                  | on the world. Here's how it unfolded and what changed for us in our house.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("24","JUN","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/02-signs-of-the-times.html", title="Signs Of The Times") Signs Of The Times
              .panel-body
                div
                  | The devil doesn't want you to see or hear the real news. Otherwise you might
                  | begin to recognise the warning signs that the bible foretells about the times in which we now live.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("16","JUN","2020")

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/blog/2020/01-walking-and-talking-with-god.html", title="Walking And Talking With God") Walking And Talking With God
              .panel-body
                div
                  | Dog walking is not so much a necessity for our dogs as an excuse for me to take pleasure in God's creation and to pray.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("07","JUN","2020")

            h2 2019

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/resources/bible-study-ephesians-1.html", title="Walking And Talking With God") Bible Study: Identity Explained
              .panel-body
                div
                  | In this bible study of Ephesians 1 a number of identities are revealed and explained, including that of
                  | our own new identity in Christ as believers.
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("04","JAN","2019")

            h2 2018

            .panel.panel-default
              .panel-heading
                a(href="/resources/the-turner-of-the-pages.html", title="The Turner Of The Pages") The Turner Of The Pages
              .panel-body
                div
                  | I was praying as I was walking when I started to have
                  | vivid thoughts about God. Here's what God had me thinking ...
                  br
                  +BLOG_DATE("27","FEB","2018")

          .col-md-4.hidden-print
            hr.featurette-divider.hidden-md.hidden-lg
            .biblenavigation.hidden-print
              h3#goto Navigate The Bible
              h4 Go To Bible Reference
              .versenavigation
                form
                  label(for='vref') Enter a bible reference (e.g. 'John 3:16' or 'Ps 23') to go to:
                  fieldset
                    input#vref(type='text', maxlength='25', spellcheck='false')
                    button#gotoverse.btn-md.btn-primary(type='submit', onclick='GoToVerse(); return false') Go
        // /row
      // /container
    include ../includes/page_footer.pug
    script(type='text/javascript', src='../script/biblenav.js')
